{"tid":270241,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"黎緊會帶呀媽同佢個朋友去東京，住邊好？","createTime":"2017-06-04T08:06:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-04T12:57:31.000Z","uid":105400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e7b479f18c75853bace046c3d9d554ebcee683eb","tid":270241,"uid":105400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T08:06:55.000Z","msg":"我去話東京一次，住新宿，覺得幾方便既因爲步行距離已經有野睇。<br />\n<br />\n因為今次有一日細佬我會離開，佢地兩個女人乜都唔識自己玩一日。其實應該住番新宿，定係揀間酒店近車站既就算？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b594ad7101df0347a322446e816674eafec469c","tid":270241,"uid":105400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T08:19:26.000Z","msg":"因為上次去，係住新宿既airbnb，但聽講依家日本禁左，所以打算住番酒店，不過就搵緊住咩位置好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8738d7b33e1172c37a59be7adc83286503502849","tid":270241,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T08:22:00.000Z","msg":"乜都唔識叫佢地去新宿即係玩死佢地姐<br />\n住其他無咁複雜嘅車站附近啦"},{"pid":"6240e8e088477b5a1d2b65f135d5a9f97a9f02a9","tid":270241,"uid":105400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T08:43:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜都唔識叫佢地去新宿即係玩死佢地姐<br />\n住其他無咁複雜嘅車站附近啦</blockquote><br />\n其實係咪總之揀一間酒店係山手線一個站就最方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7d986fc7bf4106037c6139e37a8038b3aa4081e","tid":270241,"uid":121060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T08:55:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>乜都唔識叫佢地去新宿即係玩死佢地姐<br />\n住其他無咁複雜嘅車站附近啦</blockquote><br />\n其實係咪總之揀一間酒店係山手線一個站就最方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我之前幫呀媽book 酒店，附近係有驚安之殿堂，方便佢行街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9d43123c4fc4d8077f7b57b9bf5fda6e1ca1c27","tid":270241,"uid":4374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T09:02:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n六本木幾好住"},{"pid":"adc6b055f8111c13276050bafb8e3ebe63a43ffb","tid":270241,"uid":8435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T09:25:36.000Z","msg":"你阿媽鍾唔鍾意shopping?<br />\n鍾意嘅話就新宿，至少唔使搭車都有一堆百貨公司行<br />\n最好唔好東新宿嗰邊，始終要行一段路"},{"pid":"3c23992a655389efe97b335c991b03c729212ffc","tid":270241,"uid":14509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T09:37:08.000Z","msg":"住池袋嗰邊都ok 唔會太難行"},{"pid":"45354ba52c62f68f99e57a37bc505d4c87009d79","tid":270241,"uid":6227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T12:57:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>住池袋嗰邊都ok 唔會太難行</blockquote><br />\n得女人就唔好北池袋果邊"}]}